title: Wolfram Mathematica 9.0.1 for GNU/Linux + Keygen (Win)
description:
Wolfram Mathematica 9.0.1 for GNU/Linux + Keygen (in Windows for Mathematica 8).

For Keygen you need Visual C++ 2010 redistributable package and sometimes works and another don't works. Try almost 3 times for activate it.

++++++++++++++
+++ Files: +++
++++++++++++++
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
++                                          ++
++ 1.- Mathematica_8_kg.exe (156KB)         ++
++ 2.- Mathematica_9.0.1_LINUX.sh (1.8GB)   ++
++                                          ++
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

You must make a directory on "/opt/" named "Mathematica" (/opt/Mathematica/) and put the ".sh" file into directory. Then, make a "chmod +x to .sh file" and run it with root privileges and enjoy it!.
